# 🔍 py-scrape — Codebase Analysis & Restructuring Plan

## Current State Overview

Your project is a **London Stock Exchange web scraper** that collects Form 8.3 filing data (voting rights disclosures) for companies like Blackrock. It's built with Selenium + pyShadow and outputs to CSV.

