## 📁 Proposed Restructured File Layout

```
py-scrape/
├── pyproject.toml              # Modern project config (replaces setup.py + requirements.txt)
├── README.md
├── .gitignore
│
├── config/
│   └── settings.py             # All configuration in one place
│
├── scraper/                    # Main package
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── driver.py               # Selenium driver factory (shared by all modules)
│   ├── core.py                 # Core scraping logic (from pyscrape.py, no globals)
│   ├── links.py                # Link collection (from linkscrape_v2.py)
│   └── models.py               # Company dataclass & data structures
│
├── pipeline/                   # Orchestration & processing
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── runner.py               # Pipeline orchestrator (from link_flow.py + link_analyser.py)
│   └── dedup.py                # Deduplication utility (from dupli-remove.py)
│
├── data/                       # Data files (gitignored)
│   ├── links/
│   │   └── blackrock_links.txt
│   ├── output/
│   │   └── blackrock.csv
│   └── skipped/
│       └── skipped_links.txt
│
├── tests/                      # Tests
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── test_core.py
│   └── test_links.py
│
└── main.py                     # Single entry point
```

